<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1/2 (100 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Keen Smell.</em></strong> The bear has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on smell.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Multiattack.</em></strong> The bear makes two attacks: one with its bite and one with its claws.</p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 5 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Claws.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 7 (2d4 + 2) slashing damage.</p>

